28.06	Lorenzo_Lamas	Lorenzo Lamas	Lorenzo Lamas y de Santos (born January 20, 1958) is an American actor. Lamas is known for playing Lance Cumson on the popular 1980s soap opera Falcon Crest, Reno Raines on the 1990s crime drama Renegade, and Hector Ramirez on the daytime soap opera The Bold and The Beautiful. Lamas appeared in reality television, serving as a judge on ABC television's short-lived Are You Hot? and presently starring in his own reality show, Leave it to Lamas, a series about his real-life family.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/71/Lorenzo_Lamas.jpg/220px-Lorenzo_Lamas.jpg
